v6: 
-> Added new functions:
  -> Factorial (fac) (!)
  -> Random (rnd) (return random integer between 0 & the value you enter)
-> Remade permissions:
  -> easycalculator.* = access to all the calculator
  -> easycalculator.operations = permission for accessing simple operations
  -> easycalculator.functions = permission for accessing functions operations
--------------------------------------------
v5: 
  -> Infinite calculation in a single format (e.g: =2+2+2...)
  -> Functions now properly supports decimals numbers & negatives numbers (will still fail silently if function isn't valid)
--------------------------------------------
v4: Added new functions:
    -> Power function (pow2 & pow3)
    -> Inverse trigonometric functions (arc) -> asin, acos, atan
--------------------------------------------
v3: Added functions calculations: '=function(number)'
    -> sin, cos, tan, sqrt, ln, log, exp
--------------------------------------------
v2: Added modulo (%) operations & support of negative numbers.
--------------------------------------------
v1: Initial release